{7000}{}{Hello, @pname@.}
{8000}{}{I'm a very old man and I sinned enough in my life... I wish to free my soul from sins before I'm gone. Find my daughter and bring her to me. When you return, I'll tell you about this one interesting abandoned military depot. Me and my friend found it 20 years ago, when we were trappers...}
{8010}{}{[Continue]}
{9000}{}{Bring my damn junkie daughter. She probably lives with some scumbags in the Den junkie community. Then I'll tell you where that depot is. Player has the key, he's in New Reno. As far as I know, Player still takes part in porn shooting. Damn, that bastard always loved women... And vice versa.}
{9010}{}{You aren't too lucky to have a daughter like her. We'll find her. Just don't die, for wastes sake.}
{10000}{}{Sorry, I'm busy.}
{11000}{}{That's a no go. Too few people, you won't cope with that! Go gather a bigger party, then we'll have a word.}
{12000}{}{Hmmm... Why did you bring so many people? No, no, no. Take a decision who's in and who's out.}
{13000}{}{You're not ready for such an important task yet. Come back when you grow some balls.}
{14000}{}{Me and Johnny were hunting that day, and we've gone too deep. We couldn't find a single gecko in the whole district! Those thingies just disappeared!}
{14010}{}{Go on.}
{15000}{}{That's not an easy task. You'll need a team of 6 people or so. Tell them to stand beside you. Tell me when you're ready.}
{15010}{}{No problemo, oldie. Me and my friends are ready. Weee-haaa!}
{15020}{}{No, that's insane! Forget it.}
{16000}{}{We were nearly out of food and water, and if kept going this way we'd have to return empty. That'd be shameful!}
{16010}{}{"That would be", you say. So Lady Fortune turned her face at last?}
{17000}{}{Yeah. She did. We saw a little golden gecko pride and creeped close. Johnny took the biggest lizard's eye out with his first shot. The pelt wasn't even damaged. Johnny was damn acqurate...}
{17010}{}{Was? What happened?}
{18000}{}{Keep listening. So one damn gecko, the last one alive, suddenly dived into a cave. Johnny went after him. I had a bad feeling about it. I was late a few seconds, dammit...}
{18010}{}{[You stare at the old man with your mouth open]}
{19000}{}{I failed to stop my friend. In a few seconds after he disappeared in the cave, I heard some shots. Then I saw pieces of flesh flying out of the cave. Thank god or whoever, but it was that gecko's flesh. Johnny, also known as Player now, managed to hide behind a rock ledge and ran out of the cave while turrets were reloading. Yeah. There were turrets guarding that depot.}
{19010}{}{Oh boy...}
{20000}{}{Yeah. So that's how I nearly lost a friend and found that damn depot. [You see that he's about to cry]}
{20010}{}{Okay, that's enough, oldie. I see that recalling those memories causes you pain. I'm sorry. Let's get down to the business.}

